            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "五礦地產獲控股股東提出溢價1.04倍私有化 股份今復牌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">五礦地產(00230)公布，獲控股股東五礦香港提出私有化。私有化作價每股1元，較停牌前收市價0.49元溢價約1.04倍。該股今早復牌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"五礦地產官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/MINMETAL-LAND_00230_1200_1.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"五礦地產官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/MINMETAL-LAND_00230_1200_1.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">五礦地產官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">若以該股停牌前10個交易日平均收市價0.363元計，私有化作價較之溢價達1.76倍；較該股截至6月底時未經審核綜合資產淨值每股0.358元也有溢價1.79倍。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大股東提私有化五礦地產涉及最高現金代價，將約為12.76億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">要約人(亦即大股東)表示，雖然五礦地產業務基礎穩固，但股份交易量長期低迷，價值持續被低估，限制公司從資本市場籌集資金的能力，基於外部環境具有挑戰性及複雜性，上市地位不再提供充足的離岸資金支持。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">要約人相信，私有化有助股東提供清晰及明確的退出機會，毋須承受任何因股份流動性不足而產生的折讓，亦可讓公司實施長期戰略及提升業務靈活性。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15366840-%e4%ba%94%e7%a4%a6%e5%9c%b0%e7%94%a2%e7%8d%b2%e6%8e%a7%e8%82%a1%e8%82%a1%e6%9d%b1%e6%8f%90%e5%87%ba%e6%ba%a2%e5%83%b91-04%e5%80%8d%e7%a7%81%e6%9c%89%e5%8c%96-%e8%82%a1%e4%bb%bd%e4%bb%8a%e5%be%a9",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/MINMETAL-LAND_00230_1200.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-24 08:43:14",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "普拉達今年首9個月收益淨額按年升8.9% 所有地區零售銷售淨額均有增長",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">普拉達(01913)公布，今年首9個月收益淨額40.7億歐元，按固定匯率計按年升8.9%；期內所有地區零售銷售淨額均錄得增長。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：普拉達官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250605_FI_source-web_01913.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：普拉達官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250605_FI_source-web_01913.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：普拉達官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">按品牌劃分，期內Prada品牌零售銷售淨額24.28億歐元，按年減少1.6%；Miu Miu零售銷售淨額11.78億歐元元，則按年大升41.4%。各品牌合計零售銷售淨額達36.47億歐元，較去年同期提升9.3%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">單計第3季的零售銷售淨額則按年升7.6%，當中Prada品牌按年減少0.8%，Miu Miu按年增長28.6%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">亞太區依然是提供最大零售銷售淨額的市場，今年首9個月累計達12.16億歐元，按年升10.4%；歐洲市場也有11.37億歐元，增長6.3%；美洲、日本、中東市場則分別較去年同期增長14.8%、2.6%、及21.1%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15367160-%e6%99%ae%e6%8b%89%e9%81%94%e4%bb%8a%e5%b9%b4%e9%a6%969%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88%e6%94%b6%e7%9b%8a%e6%b7%a8%e9%a1%8d%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%878-9-%e6%89%80%e6%9c%89%e5%9c%b0%e5%8d%80%e9%9b%b6%e5%94%ae",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/01913-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-24 08:30:23",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑期夜期均收復二萬六關 高水約171點 重磅港股ADR齊升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中美兩國元首將於下周四在南韓會面，加上外圍股市回升，有利港股氣氛，黑期、夜期與港股ADR指數齊收復二萬六關口。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"Shutterstock圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250416_FI_source_licensed_China_US_shutterstock_704.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"Shutterstock圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250416_FI_source_licensed_China_US_shutterstock_704.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">Shutterstock圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時14分升246點或0.95%，報26138點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股ADR指數報26051點，較香港上日現貨收市高83點或0.32%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣635.8元，較上日香港收市高2.82元或0.45%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合港幣167元，較上日香港收市高2.38元或1.45%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合港幣101元，較上日香港收市高0.98元或0.98%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合港幣128.9元，較上日香港收市高0.22元或0.17%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合港幣46.9元，較上日香港收市高0.2元或0.42%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合港幣103元，較上日香港收市高0.28元或0.27%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合港幣71.3元，較上日香港收市高0.44元或0.62%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合港幣425.5元，較上日香港收市高3.66元或0.87%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合港幣55.6元，較上日香港收市高0.09元或0.16%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合港幣7.9元，較上日香港收市高0.02元或0.19%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指夜市期指收報26139點，升182點，較上日恒指收市25967點，高水171點。科指期貨夜市收報6022點，較上日科指收市高水71點；國指期貨夜市收報9366點，較上日國指收市高水65點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15367157-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e5%a4%9c%e6%9c%9f%e5%9d%87%e6%94%b6%e5%be%a9%e4%ba%8c%e8%90%ac%e5%85%ad%e9%97%9c-%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4%e7%b4%84171%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1adr%e9%bd%8a%e5%8d%87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/ADR-1_source-bp_-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-24 08:20:23",
